what schools we've picked.

02:05.826 --> 02:08.627
Hmm, which tent
should I go to first?

02:08.629 --> 02:10.496
I know, come with me, Sofia.

02:10.498 --> 02:11.797
Where are we going?

02:11.799 --> 02:13.832
To my favorite tent,
of course.

02:13.834 --> 02:15.767
It's a school where you learn
to be in charge

02:15.769 --> 02:17.169
and tell people what to do.

02:17.171 --> 02:19.671
Hey, Desmond, are you lost?

02:19.673 --> 02:21.673
The Science and Alchemy tent
is back that way.

02:21.675 --> 02:24.309
Well, deep down, I've always
wanted to be a hero.

02:24.311 --> 02:27.813
Wait, are you really interested
in becoming a knight?

02:27.815 --> 02:30.449
