stick to books.
- Why?

02:30.451 --> 02:32.818
Because I really
don't know the first thing

02:32.820 --> 02:34.853
- about being a knight.
- It's a school!

02:34.855 --> 02:36.421
They'll teach you
how to do everything.

02:36.423 --> 02:39.691
Come on,
let's go in together.

02:39.693 --> 02:41.793
- Brilliant!
- [man] Welcome!

02:41.795 --> 02:45.831
As some of you may already know,
I am Sir Finnegan.

02:45.833 --> 02:48.867
Now, as a former student
of Chivalry Hall,

02:48.869 --> 02:50.669
they've asked me to show you

02:50.671 --> 02:52.871
what this fine school
is all about.

02:52.873 --> 02:54.873
Allow me to demonstrate

02:54.875 --> 02:57.276
the kinds of skills
you'd be learning,

02:57.278 --> 03:00.612
like how to toss a javelin!
[grunts]

03:00.614 --> 03:03.515
- Whoa!
- Amazing.

03:03.517 --> 03:08.554
Now [chuckles] who'd like
to give it a try?

03:14.562 --> 03:17.763
Impressive form,
my knights to be!

03:22.136 --> 03:25.070
Wow, it's like they're already
real knights.

03:25.072 --> 03:27.506
Want to give it a go, lad?

03:27.508 --> 03:29.908
Don't worry, Des,
those two may be good,

03:29.910 --> 03:32.077
but this isn't a competition.

03:32.079 --> 03:34.646
Come on,
what do you have to lose?

03:38.052 --> 03:39.251
[grunts]

03:42.690 --> 03:44.890
Ah, not the best effort,

03:44.892 --> 03:47.359
but if you want
to get better at it,

03:47.361 --> 03:50.062
Chivalry Hall
is the school for you.

03:50.064 --> 03:51.863
Here we are, Sofia,

03:51.865 --> 03:54.499
