you would want

04:41.215 --> 04:43.215
to represent your own kingdom.

04:43.217 --> 04:45.617
Only three?
That's tough.

04:45.619 --> 04:48.820
Indeed it is.
As is ruling a kingdom.

04:48.822 --> 04:53.125
Hmm, well, I'd want
my kingdom to have heart,

04:53.127 --> 04:54.693
so...

04:56.430 --> 05:00.599
Wow, okay,
I also can't imagine a kingdom

05:00.601 --> 05:04.136
without family and friends.

05:06.507 --> 05:11.677
