down at the same time.

07:43.397 --> 07:45.597
Oh, Sofia,
are you going to join us?

07:45.599 --> 07:49.100
I don't know.
I do love performing.

07:49.102 --> 07:51.937
But I also liked making
my coat of arms.

07:51.939 --> 07:55.173
Jun! I'm going to see
how she's doing.

07:55.175 --> 07:57.175
I'll see you guys later.

07:57.177 --> 08:01.146
