15:07.841 --> 15:10.241
Sofia, I have exciting news.

15:10.243 --> 15:13.511
I know, I know, but I still
haven't picked a school.

15:13.513 --> 15:15.513
Well, then you'll love this.

15:15.515 --> 15:18.616
Because surprise!
I picked one for you.

15:18.618 --> 15:21.719
- What?
- It's already at the wall
waiting to be carved in stone.

15:21.721 --> 15:23.621
Amber, how could you?

15:23.623 --> 15:25.256
Time was almost up,

15:25.258 --> 15:26.925
and you had to put
something down.

15:26.927 --> 15:28.726
I figured since
you had to go somewhere,

15:28.728 --> 15:30.929
the best place was with me.

15:30.931 --> 15:32.730
But I like other schools, too.

15:32.732 --> 15:35.800
Well, you have to pick one.
That's the rules.

15:35.802 --> 15:38.436
That doesn't mean you get
to choose my school for me.

15:38.438 --> 15:41.606
- I need to fix this.
- Sofia, wait!

15:41.608 --> 15:43.708
[crash]

15:53.586 --> 15:55.720
Is there anyone inside
that armor?

15:55.722 --> 15:57.288
Doesn't look like it.

15:57.290 --> 15:58.489
Then how is it dueling?

15:58.491 --> 16:00.558
The only thing
that could possibly cause that

16:00.560 --> 16:03.628
- is a come-to-lifeium potion.
- A what?

16:03.630 --> 16:06.397
It's a potion that makes
inanimate objects come to life.

16:06.399 --> 16:08.066
Some must have spilled
on the armor.

16:11.338 --> 16:13.838
Sofia, look out!

16:17.677 --> 16:19.577
Hold on, Sof, I'm coming!

16:24.184 --> 16:26.150
I'll make a potion to stop it!

16:29.689 --> 16:32.156
Oh, please, let me pass.

16:34.094 --> 16:36.694
Look, Mr. Knight,
there's a tablet

16:36.696 --> 16:38.696
with my face on it
that I really need to find.

16:38.698 --> 16:41.599
Ah! Oh, boy.

16:43.703 --> 16:45.503
Here, take this!

16:52.946 --> 16:55.747
Here, pour this on the armor.

17:04.190 --> 17:06.891
Thanks, guys, I owe you one.

17:09.963 --> 17:11.629
Well done, lads.

17:11.631 --> 17:15.400
Now that was quick thinking
on your part, Prince Desmond.

17:15.402 --> 17:18.169
I didn't do anything.
James poured the potion.

17:18.171 --> 17:19.804
Which you made.

17:19.806 --> 17:22.240
I never would've stopped
that armor if it wasn't for you.

17:22.242 --> 17:24.542
- You're a hero!
- But I'm not a knight.

17:24.544 --> 17:28.346
No one ever said you had
to be a knight to be a hero.

17:28.348 --> 17:30.648
That's right,
you're a hero alchemist.

17:30.650 --> 17:34.252
Indeed, and there is
a long tradition of alchemists

17:34.254 --> 17:37.622
and knights working together
to save kingdoms.

17:39.592 --> 17:45.263
Welcome to the finale
of the Royal School Fair,

17:45.265 --> 17:49.767
the unveiling
of the Wall of Next Steps.

17:49.769 --> 17:53.938
[fanfare plays]

17:53.940 --> 17:55.039
I'm too late.

17:55.041 --> 17:58.409
The curtain, if you will.

17:58.411 --> 17:59.477
Oh, no!

18:02.682 --> 18:04.882
As you can see on our wall,

18:04.884 --> 18:07.618
each member
of our graduating class

18:07.620 --> 18:12.223
has chosen where they will go
after they leave Royal Prep.

18:12.225 --> 18:15.626
So, children, come forward

18:15.628 --> 18:18.029
and see
what your fellow students

18:18.031 --> 18:21.532
have chosen
for their next schools.

18:21.534 --> 18:24.268
Wow, Zoe, you're going to
the School for Adventure?

18:24.270 --> 18:25.603
Well, where else would I go?

18:25.605 --> 18:28.773
Oh, Chivalry Hall.
Way to go, James!

18:28.775 --> 18:31.809
Khalid, you're going to
the School of Royal Fashions?

18:31.811 --> 18:33.811
Surprise!

18:33.813 --> 18:35.913
[gasps]
EverRealm Academy!

18:35.915 --> 18:37.748
Congratulations, Amber.

18:37.750 --> 18:39.784
You're following
in your family's footsteps.

18:39.786 --> 18:41.252
What about you, Hildy?

18:41.254 --> 18:44.655
Oh, the School
for Royal Fashions, of course.

18:44.657 --> 18:47.291
It'll be weird going
to a different school

18:47.293 --> 18:48.659
than you, Hildy.

18:48.661 --> 18:50.761
I know
that you're mad at me, but--

18:50.763 --> 18:53.631
Actually, Cleo,
you made the right choice.

18:53.633 --> 18:56.734
You were born to perform.
I'll miss you.

18:56.736 --> 18:58.469
I'll miss you, too, Hildy.

18:58.471 --> 19:00.671
Sofia, you're going
to EverRealm Academy?

19:00.673 --> 19:01.639
Amazing.

19:01.641 --> 19:03.174
No, I'm not.

19:03.176 --> 19:04.909
Sofia, what are you doing?

19:04.911 --> 19:06.777
But it says so right there.

19:06.779 --> 19:07.845
No, it doesn't.

19:07.847 --> 19:09.280
It does so!

19:09.282 --> 19:11.349
No, Amber, it doesn't.

19:12.785 --> 19:14.986
I didn't choose that school.

19:14.988 --> 19:17.388
I'm going to erase it.

19:20.627 --> 19:22.193
[all gasp]

19:22.195 --> 19:24.929
Children, well,
what's going on here?

19:24.931 --> 19:28.299
Sofia,
what happened to the wall?

19:28.301 --> 19:30.368
I'm sorry,
Miss Merryweather,

19:30.370 --> 19:32.670
but the truth is
I like all the schools.

19:32.672 --> 19:34.772
I don't want to pick just one.

19:34.774 --> 19:39.143
I'm sure this is all
a big misunderstanding.

19:39.145 --> 19:41.679
You had the most fun
with me at EverRealm.

19:41.681 --> 19:43.147
Right, Sofia?

19:43.149 --> 19:45.516
I had fun
at all the schools today.

19:45.518 --> 19:48.819
So? Which school do you want
to go to then?

19:48.821 --> 19:51.789
Sofia, it's a simple question.

19:51.791 --> 19:54.959
It's not simple at all.
That's the problem.

19:58.898 --> 20:02.366
At first, I was really excited
about the fair,

20:02.368 --> 20:04.202
but it's too big a decision.

20:04.204 --> 20:06.037
I don't know
what I want to do.

20:06.039 --> 20:09.540
You know, I'm not really sure
what I want to do either.

20:09.542 --> 20:11.709
- You're not?
- Not really.

20:11.711 --> 20:13.811
I just put something down
so I wouldn't miss out.

20:13.813 --> 20:15.313
Me too.

20:15.315 --> 20:17.748
[sighs] I'm so glad
I'm not the only one.

20:17.750 --> 20:19.917
It's too hard
to decide in one day.

20:19.919 --> 20:21.719
I wish
we didn't have to pick.

20:21.721 --> 20:23.854
Children, please, please.

20:23.856 --> 20:26.891
This tradition exists
for a reason.

20:26.893 --> 20:29.894
There comes a time
in each of our lives

20:29.896 --> 20:32.496
where we all
must make a choice.

20:32.498 --> 20:35.733
But that doesn't mean
your choice has to last forever.

20:35.735 --> 20:38.936
Did you know that
once upon a time,

20:38.938 --> 20:41.939
I wanted to be
a tooth fairy?

20:41.941 --> 20:45.109
- You did?
- That was my first choice.

20:45.111 --> 20:49.280
But after a while,
I found a different path,

20:49.282 --> 20:51.849
and perhaps so shall you.

20:51.851 --> 20:53.017
Ladies?

21:02.762 --> 21:07.798
In keeping with tradition,
you must all make a choice.

21:07.800 --> 21:13.104
But if you're not sure,
you can always change your mind.

21:14.774 --> 21:17.541
So go forth and write

21:17.543 --> 21:20.244
whatever school you wish
on this wall.

21:20.246 --> 21:24.048
And no matter what we choose,
it won't be forever?

21:24.050 --> 21:25.883
Oh, nothing is, my dear.

21:28.588 --> 21:31.389
Sofia, I hope
you're not mad at me.

21:31.391 --> 21:34.659
It's just we're all going off
in different directions,

21:34.661 --> 21:38.596
and I didn't want that
for you and me.

21:38.598 --> 21:41.799
It's okay, Amber.
I know you were trying to help.

21:41.801 --> 21:44.468
But how about next time
asking

21:44.470 --> 21:46.937
before making such a big
decision for someone else?

21:46.939 --> 21:48.973
Great idea.

21:48.975 --> 21:52.009
So which school
<i> are</i> you picking?

21:57.984 --> 21:59.784
Actually, Amber,

21:59.786 --> 22:02.653
I think I'll be happy
with you at EverRealm.

22:02.655 --> 22:04.522
For now.

22:04.524 --> 22:05.823
Yes!

22:05.825 --> 22:09.093
[laughs]
Well, I'm glad that's settled

22:09.095 --> 22:11.028
because it's time to celebrate.

22:11.030 --> 22:13.197
[all]
<i> ¶ Congratulations ¶</i>

22:13.199 --> 22:15.099
<i> ¶ Congratulations ¶</i>

22:15.101 --> 22:18.836
<i> ¶ Congratulations to us all ¶</i>

22:18.838 --> 22:21.005
<i> ¶ Congratulations ¶</i>

22:21.007 --> 22:22.873
<i> ¶ Congratulations ¶</i>

22:22.875 --> 22:24.809
<i> ¶ Congratulations ¶</i>

22:24.811 --> 22:29.880
<i> ¶ To us a-a-ll ¶</i>

